
1. Ientify the pair of customers who live in same city?

SELECT 
  c.CustomerName, 
  cc.CustomerName
FROM Customers as c
INNER JOIN Customers as cc
  ON c.Country = cc.Country
  AND c.customerID != cc.customerID
;

2. Find the Customers who spent most on their orders?

SELECT 
  CustomerName,
  Sum(price) as Total_spent
FROM Customers as C
INNER JOIN Orders as O
  ON C.CustomerID = O.CustomerID
INNER JOIN Products as P
  ON O.ProductID = P.ProductID
Group By CustomerName
Order BY Sum(price) DESC
Limit 1;

3. Find the Customers who have ordered more than one type of products ?

SELECT 
  C.CustomerName
FROM Customers as C
INNER JOIN Orders as O
  ON C.CustomerID = O.CustomerID
Group By C.CustomerName
Having Count(OrderID) > 1;

